BTCPoolman is a [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]].

This pool initially pays out a proportional share, and is implementing a Pay-per-Share (PPS)  reward systems.

The service was first publicly available on March 01, 2013 and it supports getwork and stratum.

##Reward distribution

* Initially Proportional, once we have blocks mined, Pay-per-Share: 2% fee.

##Mining Protocols

* Getwork servers
* Stratum servers (preferred)


